data.description: Tucked away in a quiet neighborhood in highly sought after Deep Creek area. This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home nestled in the back of the neighborhood on a large wooded lot is ready for new owners!. Lots of privacy and no rear neighbors! Large family room has a wood burning fireplace. Formal living room has french doors making it a great fit for an office or playroom. Updated kitchen has granite counter tops, pantry and stainless appliances. Upstairs you’ll find a large primary suite that has 2 walk-in closets, a linen closet and en suite bathroom.  A finished room above the garage serves as the 4th bedroom with a full bathroom at the bottom of the stairs. Brand new fence enclosing the large backyard, with an above ground pool for your family to enjoy.  Come see it before it's gone!
